    "work_description": "The proposal is to divide the site into 6 lots. An existing house will be preserved on Lot 1. A new private street is proposed to provide access and frontage to all lots. The resource area of the environmental zone will be placed within Tract B, the environmental resource tract. All environmental standards are proposed to be met; therefore, Environmental Review is not required. Stormwater treatment will be via shared planters with overflow to the drainage on the northern boundary of the site; the planters will be located within Tract A, the Private Street and Stormwater Tract.",
